    <summary>Specifies which scroll bars will be visible on a control.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 This enumeration is used by <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox.ScrollBars%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.  
  
 Not all controls support scroll bars. Use this enumeration to specify which scroll bars will be visible on a control, either under some or all circumstances.  
  
   
  
